01:22:49,058 --> 01:22:53,812
You and the rest of you dreamers
want to piss it up against the wall!

511
01:22:53,937 --> 01:22:56,356
Not everybody can fight.

512
01:22:56,481 --> 01:22:58,900
There are those who must organise
co-ordinate.

513
01:22:59,025 --> 01:23:01,111
Yes yes of course.

514
01:23:03,738 --> 01:23:06,032
Yeah well...

515
01:23:06,157 --> 01:23:08,243
...don't pay any attention to me.

516
01:23:09,452 --> 01:23:12,163
It's personal.

517
01:23:22,756 --> 01:23:25,551
Sorry about those orders. I'm staying.

518
01:23:27,261 --> 01:23:29,930
I don't give a fuck about your revolutions.

519
01:23:30,055 --> 01:23:35,311
I'm tired of running up and down these
mountains and getting nowhere so I've stopped.

520
01:23:35,436 --> 01:23:38,730
Right here at the bridge of San Jorge.

521
01:23:41,441 --> 01:23:46,029
Maybe it's out of spite for you
and your slow dream or maybe...

522
01:23:47,947 --> 01:23:50,491
Ah maybe my feet are sore.

523
01:24:08,383 --> 01:24:14,431
'Hombres' Me and irlandés are gonna catch
ourselves a couple of fucking locusts.

524
01:24:14,556 --> 01:24:15,807
(commotion)

525
01:24:15,932 --> 01:24:19,561
'Atente' You go back and hide in the grotto.

526
01:24:19,686 --> 01:24:23,731
If things go bad here every man for himself.

527
01:24:23,856 --> 01:24:26,734
You move your asses! ¿ Comprenden?

528
01:24:28,527 --> 01:24:30,363
(men shout)

529
01:24:58,598 --> 01:25:03,895
If something happens
and your father doesn't come back

530
01:25:04,020 --> 01:25:08,525
then I pray that the great God in heaven
takes care of you.

531
01:25:33,298 --> 01:25:37,135
Well... Good luck.

532
01:25:37,260 --> 01:25:38,928
Thank you.

533
01:25:59,948 --> 01:26:02,159
(men shout)

534
01:26:02,284 --> 01:26:07,497
Listen when they are out of sight
we will make a run for it. ¿ SÍ?

535
01:26:15,172 --> 01:26:21,177
No? You can't mean to stay here? All those
explosions must have gone to your head!

536
01:26:25,014 --> 01:26:28,684
Remember John and Juan?

537
01:26:30,186 --> 01:26:31,979
America.

538
01:26:32,938 --> 01:26:34,815
The millions.

539
01:26:37,985 --> 01:26:39,570
No.

540
01:26:40,613 --> 01:26:44,658
I don't understand!
Wasn't that was a trick for us to get out?

541
01:26:44,783 --> 01:26:49,746
- What can we do against those locusts?
- You'd be doing me a favour if you'd leave.

542
01:26:49,871 --> 01:26:55,961
If I had a choice between a chicken thief
and ridding the world of a few uniforms

543
01:26:56,086 --> 01:26:58,380
I'd not choose the chicken thief.

544
01:27:01,132 --> 01:27:02,717
OK.

545
01:27:06,053 --> 01:27:07,930
OK.

546
01:27:09,223 --> 01:27:10,933
No!

547
01:27:11,058 --> 01:27:13,185
(laughs)

548
01:27:13,310 --> 01:27:16,814
Oh no no. You will like that huh?

549
01:27:17,606 --> 01:27:24,530
Well you listen to me you Irish piece of shit!

550
01:27:25,197 --> 01:27:30,118
You think you're the only man
with the balls to stay? You are wrong!

551
01:27:30,243 --> 01:27:33,746
I have the balls and I stay.

552
01:27:53,015 --> 01:27:57,728
He says there's no danger
just watch the bridge from a long way.

553
01:27:58,937 --> 01:28:03,984
No matter how I look with them
I'm still too close to the bridge.

554
01:28:05,027 --> 01:28:08,280
Why am I mixed up in this revolution anyway?

555
01:28:08,405 --> 01:28:14,493
God why didn't you strike me down
instead of letting me say "I stay too"?

556
01:28:15,453 --> 01:28:19,290
Oh look at him! All because of him.

557
01:28:19,415 --> 01:28:22,293
He acts like a tourist only he's staying.

558
01:28:22,418 --> 01:28:24,920
(laughs) Look at him.

559
01:28:25,046 --> 01:28:27,757
What the hell does he care?

560
01:28:27,882 --> 01:28:30,343
He is having fun.

561
01:28:30,468 --> 01:28:35,014
I'm glad he's having fun God
because I am not having fun.

562
01:28:35,139 --> 01:28:37,265
Oh-ho no.

563
01:28:41,019 --> 01:28:42,270
Hey...

564
01:28:43,647 --> 01:28:46,024
What's this?

565
01:28:50,695 --> 01:28:52,989
Now he goes to sleep huh?

566
01:28:53,531 --> 01:28:57,160
Go ahead you sleep sleep.

567
01:28:57,953 --> 01:29:01,956
I tell you something when he's asleep I'll go.
Shh!

568
01:29:19,098 --> 01:29:21,183
(laughs)

569
01:29:54,798 --> 01:29:56,967
Stop over there Sergeant.

570
01:30:25,911 --> 01:30:27,788
Hey!

571
01:30:31,792 --> 01:30:35,795
God only an idiot could sleep at a time like this!

572
01:30:40,133 --> 01:30:41,760
Hey!

573
01:30:54,356 --> 01:30:57,316
(clatter of hooves)

574
