All of them.

582
01:37:48,919 --> 01:37:51,295
Six.

583
01:37:54,799 --> 01:37:58,302
I've never counted them before.

584
01:39:44,071 --> 01:39:46,447
No Juan no.

585
01:39:46,572 --> 01:39:50,159
No for Christ's sake.
They're waiting for you out there.

586
01:40:38,747 --> 01:40:41,125
(rapid gunfire)

587
01:41:07,108 --> 01:41:09,193
(gunfire continues)

588
01:41:38,096 --> 01:41:40,182
(lull in gunfire)

589
01:41:42,558 --> 01:41:44,977
(gunfire recommences)

590
01:41:46,270 --> 01:41:48,606
(gunfire continues)

591
01:42:32,398 --> 01:42:34,483
(gunfire ceases)

592
01:42:37,278 --> 01:42:39,446
