593
01:42:39,571 --> 01:42:41,657
'Capitán'

594
01:42:42,700 --> 01:42:44,326
(shouting in Spanish)

595
01:42:44,451 --> 01:42:48,247
(man) Hold it!
Move that bastard out of the truck.

596
01:42:48,372 --> 01:42:51,374
(man) See that he gets to the camp alive!

597
01:42:51,499 --> 01:42:53,710
(truck moves away)

598
01:43:46,427 --> 01:43:48,804
