600
01:46:01,222 --> 01:46:03,558
'Uno dos uno'

601
01:46:12,776 --> 01:46:16,780
'Uno dos uno dos'

602
01:46:21,659 --> 01:46:24,870
'Uno dos uno dos uno dos'

